{{Otheruses|Great Hunt}}
The '''great hunt''' was the third part of the [[Crowning Convocation]]s on [[Siline]]. It involved the combatants to hunt the [[ericadi]], the planet's most dangerous predator. If multiple winners emerged, they would duel until only one remained. In earlier times these competitions had been [[Death|deadly]], but in more recent times, partially due to environmental concerns, the ericadi were tagged instead of killed and the combatants could use [[Hummer (Siline)|hummer]]s in emergencies, that would ward the ericadi off. The more recent great hunts took place in the [[hunting arena]].<ref name="TCC">''[[The Acolyte: The Crystal Crown]]''</ref>

